  <brief_title>TROPHY - Candesartan Cilexetil Long-term Hypertension Prevention Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multicenter, Long-term Trial of Preventing Hypertension Using Candesartan Cilexetil 16 mg in Patients With High Normal Blood Pressure (TROPHY)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>AstraZeneca</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effectiveness of candesartan cilexetil in
      preventing hypertension in people with high normal blood pressure. Patients will be
      randomized to either Candesartan or placebo for an initial 2-year period followed by a second
      2-year period of placebo for all patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
